00:11:58,494 --> 00:12:05,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nobody knows exactly how best</i>
<i>to merge to safely avoid crashing.</i></b></font>

141
00:12:05,744 --> 00:12:11,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That guy knows it's more dangerous</i>
<i>for him, yet he keeps coming after me.</i></b></font>

142
00:12:11,844 --> 00:12:15,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You can keep walking that</i>
<i>razor's edge till the very end!</i></b></font>

143
00:13:19,044 --> 00:13:21,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For this race...</b></font>

144
00:13:21,314 --> 00:13:24,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...it was only the day before yesterday
that I received specific information</b></font>

145
00:13:24,054 --> 00:13:28,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>regarding what tactics
our opponents would use.</b></font>

146
00:13:28,024 --> 00:13:31,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To be honest, I thought
perhaps we'd be in trouble.</b></font>

147
00:13:31,594 --> 00:13:34,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This mistake is on me.</b></font>

148
00:13:34,894 --> 00:13:38,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mistake? Even you make mistakes?</b></font>

149
00:13:38,594 --> 00:13:45,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Frequently. I bluff my way through it,
but inside I'm on pins and needles.</b></font>

150
00:13:45,234 --> 00:13:47,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>However...</b></font>

151
00:13:47,274 --> 00:13:50,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This time, luck is on my side.</b></font>

152
00:13:50,674 --> 00:13:57,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An uncertainty that no one could have
calculated may cancel out my mistake.</b></font>

153
00:13:57,114 --> 00:13:59,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An uncertainty?</b></font>

154
00:14:08,624 --> 00:14:12,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't understand it...</i>
<i>The meaning of Ryosuke's advice.</i></b></font>

155
00:14:15,304 --> 00:14:19,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The "methods"of Kyoichi of Team</i>
<i>Emperor? What were they again?</i></b></font>

156
00:14:25,474 --> 00:14:29,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ryosuke said to catch up on the</i>
<i>straightaways, but that's impossible.</i></b></font>

157
00:14:29,614 --> 00:14:31,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What do I do?!</i></b></font>

158
00:14:31,654 --> 00:14:34,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There's no way to beat an opponent</i>
<i>you can't even catch up to!</i></b></font>

159
00:14:50,304 --> 00:14:54,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The uncertainty was this rain.</b></font>

160
00:14:54,104 --> 00:14:58,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So you think the rain will give
Fujiwara the advantage?</b></font>

161
00:14:58,814 --> 00:15:02,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But that goes against popular theory.</b></font>

162
00:15:02,684 --> 00:15:04,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Rain reduces the MU of the road's surface,</b></font>

163
00:15:04,784 --> 00:15:07,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and if the tires' grip weakens uncontrollably,</b></font>

164
00:15:07,984 --> 00:15:10,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>a major handicap will become even greater.</b></font>

165
00:15:10,424 --> 00:15:12,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think that would be the standard conclusion.</b></font>

166
00:15:15,594 --> 00:15:17,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're overlooking something.</b></font>

167
00:15:17,934 --> 00:15:22,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That theory holds true for a midday
race at someplace like a circuit...</b></font>

168
00:15:22,774 --> 00:15:26,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but nighttime on a rainy
mountain pass is a different story.</b></font>

169
00:15:26,604 --> 00:15:31,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In conditions such as those, the emphasis
shifts from the car to the driver.</b></font>

170
00:15:31,644 --> 00:15:37,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Also, the X factor, or ability beyond that of
mere driving techniques, is called into play.</b></font>

171
00:15:37,354 --> 00:15:39,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>X factor?</b></font>

172
00:15:39,184 --> 00:15:41,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Therein lies our chance.</b></font>

173
00:15:41,554 --> 00:15:47,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This rain will change the hurdle I
thought too high to just the right height</b></font>

174
00:15:47,064 --> 00:15:50,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and is the uncertainty of which I spoke.</b></font>

175
00:15:50,994 --> 00:15:56,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Perhaps this rain is a blessing, made to fall
by the powerful luck that Fujiwara possesses.</b></font>

176
00:16:01,404 --> 00:16:04,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can close the gap a bit on the</i>
<i>latter half of the straightaways.</i></b></font>

177
00:16:07,584 --> 00:16:11,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Does that mean that at least on extended</i>
<i>straightaways, I have the advantage?</i></b></font>

178
00:16:11,754 --> 00:16:16,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This really is a first. Winning in</i>
<i>power but losing at cornering...</i></b></font>

179
00:16:16,894 --> 00:16:20,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's sort of pitiful. This is stressing me out.</i></b></font>

180
00:16:20,994 --> 00:16:25,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>To think, having no choice but to battle it</i>
<i>out on a mountain downhill straightaway!</i></b></font>

181
00:16:31,534 --> 00:16:35,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The way he moves so effortlessly...</i>
<i>I'm getting more and more pissed off!</i></b></font>

182
00:16:35,444 --> 00:16:38,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Whatever it takes, I wanna catch</i>
<i>up and put the pressure on him!</i></b></font>

183
00:16:41,544 --> 00:16:46,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Oh! Kyoichi's "methods"...</i>
<i>Maybe he meant that!</i></b></font>

184
00:16:59,134 --> 00:17:03,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unreal! Cappuccinos are that fast?!</b></font>

185
00:17:03,134 --> 00:17:05,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six is undefeated, but...</b></font>

186
00:17:05,574 --> 00:17:09,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Project D's ace downhill racer can't catch up?!</b></font>

187
00:17:19,624 --> 00:17:23,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He meant Kyoichi's specialty</i>
<i>technique, no doubt about it.</i></b></font>

188
00:17:25,594 --> 00:17:29,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm going to have to close the gap to pull it off.</i></b></font>

189
00:17:29,564 --> 00:17:32,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Just watch, I'll friggin' catch up to you!</i></b></font>

190
00:17:51,484 --> 00:17:54,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, understood. Thank you.</b></font>

191
00:17:55,454 --> 00:18:01,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They've just passed the road cut hairpin.
There's a 10-15 meter gap between them.</b></font>

192
00:18:06,934 --> 00:18:09,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't understand it.</i></b></font>

193
00:18:09,774 --> 00:18:13,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The Eight-Six being able to keep up with</i>
<i>the Cappuccino this far is most unusual.</i></b></font>

194
00:18:24,054 --> 00:18:27,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>In my simulations,</i>
<i>this event was an impossibility.</i></b></font>

195
00:18:27,984 --> 00:18:32,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Was the rain not to our advantage after all?</i></b></font>

196
00:18:32,024 --> 00:18:36,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If the race cannot be settled at the</i>
<i>decisive, steeply inclined section,</i></b></font>

197
00:18:36,334 --> 00:18:40,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>the gently inclined, mid- to high-speed</i>
<i>section in the latter half shall be worrisome.</i></b></font>

198
00:18:43,974 --> 00:18:46,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I miscalculated.</b></font>

199
00:18:46,574 --> 00:18:49,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The capabilities of the Eight-Six's
driver cannot be calculated.</b></font>

200
00:18:49,714 --> 00:18:54,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They've upset what was thought
to be a 100% probability of victory.</b></font>

201
00:19:05,494 --> 00:19:10,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I get it. The Eight-Six's</i>
<i>whole body is telling me.</i></b></font>

202
00:19:10,594 --> 00:19:18,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The slight sensation of the tires slipping as</i>
<i>they grip wet asphalt... It's almost palpable!</i></b></font>

203
00:19:18,004 --> 00:19:23,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I feel like with this car, I can even know</i>
<i>how much rain is flowing on the asphalt.</i></b></font>

204
00:19:25,044 --> 00:19:27,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can definitely catch up to him!</i></b></font>

205
00:19:29,754 --> 00:19:34,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll have one chance, two at the most,</i>
<i>to set up a counterattack.</i></b></font>

206
00:19:41,124 --> 00:19:44,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's one thing that's got me anxious.</b></font>

207
00:19:44,634 --> 00:19:50,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The first thing that comes to mind about
Sudou from Team Emperor is a counterattack.</b></font>

208
00:19:50,304 --> 00:19:52,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Indeed.</b></font>

209
00:19:52,034 --> 00:19:57,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm worried what sort of judgment Fujiwara
will make with his mind so confused...</b></font>

210
00:19:57,244 --> 00:20:00,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...because a counterattack would be a mistake.</b></font>

211
00:20:00,284 --> 00:20:03,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Exactly. True to form, you understand.</b></font>

212
00:20:03,914 --> 00:20:08,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A counterattack is 100% doomed to failure.</b></font>

213
00:20:31,414 --> 00:20:33,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's gaining on me!</i></b></font>

214
00:20:39,684 --> 00:20:42,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Wataru's Eight-Six couldn't</i>
<i>keep up with this car.</i></b></font>

215
00:20:42,824 --> 00:20:47,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't get it! How can he</i>
<i>be this fast in the rain?!</i></b></font>

216
00:20:48,594 --> 00:20:52,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even I am struggling, searching for grip</i>
<i>on front tires that can't be relied upon.</i></b></font>

217
00:20:52,934 --> 00:20:55,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't do any more than this!</i></b></font>

218
00:20:55,004 --> 00:20:57,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's scaring even me!</i></b></font>

219
00:20:57,934 --> 00:21:00,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This isn't logic... It's instinct.</i></b></font>

220
00:21:18,454 --> 00:21:20,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Rain sure is terrible...</b></font>

221
00:21:20,794 --> 00:21:27,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even an F1 racer with godlike
technique would spin out in the rain</b></font>

222
00:21:27,304 --> 00:21:30,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and fly right out of the course.</b></font>

223
00:21:30,004 --> 00:21:32,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's how difficult rain is.</b></font>

224
00:21:32,734 --> 00:21:36,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How it falls can change each
and every racing condition,</b></font>

225
00:21:36,144 --> 00:21:38,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and there's no telling when it'll stop.</b></font>

226
00:21:38,214 --> 00:21:41,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One mistake on this
narrow road, and it's <i>boom.</i></b></font>

227
00:21:41,544 --> 00:21:46,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even so, you have to pull yourself together
and go on the offensive, or you'll lose.</b></font>

228
00:21:46,384 --> 00:21:52,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a continuous battle between fear and
motivation. Especially on the downhill.</b></font>

229
00:21:52,024 --> 00:21:55,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It takes ten times more out
of you than a normal race.</b></font>

230
00:22:01,834 --> 00:22:05,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Dammit! What the hell are you?!</i></b></font>

231
00:22:05,004 --> 00:22:08,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I feel sick. He keeps gaining on me...</i></b></font>

232
00:22:08,374 --> 00:22:10,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What does this mean?!</i></b></font>

233
00:22:15,544 --> 00:22:21,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I think this was how it played out...</i>
<i>The race against Kyoichi at Iroha Slope.</i></b></font>

234
00:22:38,034 --> 00:22:40,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>When your opponent has</i>
<i>better cornering speed,</i></b></font>

235
00:22:40,704 --> 00:22:43,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>you have to abandon the corner attack.</i></b></font>

236
00:22:43,544 --> 00:22:49,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Slow down, quickly change the car's direction,</i>
<i>then speed up the acceleration timing!</i></b></font>

237
00:22:49,384 --> 00:22:52,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I have to spend just a little</i>
<i>more time stepping on the gas.</i></b></font>

238
00:23:09,404 --> 00:23:13,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's something I just can't accept.</b></font>

239
00:23:13,144 --> 00:23:16,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This "Shame and reputation be damned,
I came to win!" attitude really ticks me off.</b></font>

240
00:23:16,744 --> 00:23:19,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Because on the downhill,
being light is an incredible weapon.</b></font>

241
00:23:19,784 --> 00:23:23,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I couldn't stand losing to these guys!</b></font>

242
00:23:23,614 --> 00:23:27,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If we friggin' lose, I'm kicking Fujiwara's ass.</b></font>

243
00:23:27,024 --> 00:23:28,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's just like you, Keisuke...</b></font>

244
00:23:28,924 --> 00:23:33,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, there's no mistaking
we're in a tight situation.</b></font>

245
00:23:33,164 --> 00:23:38,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My only hope is that there's some
reason Ryosuke wished for this rain.</b></font>

246
00:23:38,834 --> 00:23:43,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If we can at least make it to
the midpoint, there may be hope.</b></font>

247
00:23:43,004 --> 00:23:44,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If Fujiwara makes it to the bottom,</b></font>

248
00:23:44,874 --> 00:23:48,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the roads aren't too steep
and there are long, straight lines.</b></font>

249
00:23:48,974 --> 00:23:52,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Ironic, isn't it?
--You said it.</b></font>

250
00:23:52,144 --> 00:23:54,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The downward slope has been
the only thing in his favor</b></font>

251
00:23:54,814 --> 00:24:00,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>as Fujiwara has gone up against
some powerful enemies, but this time...</b></font>

252
00:24:00,184 --> 00:24:06,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...far from being his friend, that slope
will put him through the wringer.</b></font>

253
00:24:24,874 --> 00:24:28,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Does this guy not feel fear?!</i></b></font>

254
00:24:28,084 --> 00:24:32,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Up this close, the shower of water</i>
<i>droplets obstructs your headlights.</i></b></font>

255
00:24:32,554 --> 00:24:36,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I hate that, which was the main</i>
<i>reason I chose to race in front!</i></b></font>

256
00:24:36,254 --> 00:24:40,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Driving in the night rain is bad enough,</i>
<i>but with the spray of water I'm sending up</i></b></font>

257
00:24:40,594 --> 00:24:43,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>his field of vision should be</i>
<i>hopelessly obstructed, and yet...!</i></b></font>

258
00:24:53,504 --> 00:24:55,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's right up on me!</i></b></font>

259
00:24:55,174 --> 00:24:57,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Why?! He should be completely</i>
<i>unable to see from that side ditch,</i></b></font>

260
00:24:57,514 --> 00:25:00,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>so how can he keep up with me so precisely?!</i></b></font>

261
00:25:03,114 --> 00:25:06,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You son of a bitch, you're not human!</i></b></font>

262
00:25:21,204 --> 00:25:25,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A rose that's bloomed on the battlefield,</i>
<i>for the reason they don't know</i></b></font>

263
00:25:25,204 --> 00:25:29,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A caterpillar that can only move forward</i>
<i>tramples it under foot again today</i></b></font>

264
00:25:29,074 --> 00:25:33,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yo, hates and pain, increasing only hatred</i></b></font>

265
00:25:33,384 --> 00:25:37,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hates and pain, with those</i>
<i>social conditions transmitted live</i></b></font>

266
00:25:37,484 --> 00:25:46,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hold me with stronger hands</i></b></font>

267
00:25:46,224 --> 00:25:52,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Your voice in a restless night</i>
<i>(For the reason they don't know)</i></b></font>

268
00:25:52,394 --> 00:25:58,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The world will someday be shedding blood</i>
<i>(All around the world)</i></b></font>

269
00:25:58,474 --> 00:26:08,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Let me forget that kind of news,</i>
<i>I don't want to understand</i></b></font>

270
00:26:09,584 --> 00:26:16,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nobody reason, nobody sure where is the end</i></b></font>

271
00:26:16,624 --> 00:26:25,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ah, sing gently just a little more, even if it's a lie</i></b></font>

272
00:26:25,164 --> 00:26:29,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Check it, conflicting information is</i>
<i>already reported by the mass media</i></b></font>

273
00:26:29,164 --> 00:26:33,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The outnumbered convey the</i>
<i>deep fears of the whole situation</i></b></font>

274
00:26:33,204 --> 00:26:37,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Reason is flammable, an age</i>
<i>lacking the power of restraint, yeah</i></b></font>

